data.description: JAW-DROPPING MOUNTAIN VIEWS and numerous upgrades abound throughout this immaculate 4 bed, 3 bath home! Come revel in this home???s: brand new roof, AC, the newly finished basement, custom paint throughout, an ADT security system, new kitchen cabinet hardware, upgraded black appliances, a walk-in pantry, ceiling fans throughout, a custom built-in bench/storage area in the mudroom/laundry room, custom bathroom shelving, upgraded bathroom lighting, an electric fireplace/entertainment center, a sump pump, a concrete patio, a built-in outdoor fire pit, front and rear auto sprinkler system, and the list goes on and on. Enjoy the open-concept kitchen/dining/living room complete with breathtaking mountain views, a large living room, an upgraded kitchen (inclusive of an expansive counter bar), a dining room, and a large living room. Next, enjoy the tastefully appointed half-bath, a large laundry/mudroom room (complete with a custom built-in), and a sprawling family room (complete with an electric fireplace/entertainment center, overlooking the large, level backyard). Next, make your way upstairs to enjoy the private master (complete with a beautiful en suite, custom shelving, a large walk-in closet, and room for a sitting area). Two more bedrooms, as well as a full bath complete the upper level. Make your way downstairs to enjoy the oversized junior suite/mother-in-law suite (with ample closet/storage, a full wardrobe, a separate living room, and a full bathroom). Finally, make your way out to the three-car tandem garage, as well as outside where you will appreciate the fully fenced backyard (highlighting a built-in fire pit, a trampoline, a playset, automatic sprinklers, and a concrete patio)! This home is sure to impress and is not to be missed!
